name: Recur-project
tagline: Web application that tracks a user's subscription fees.
body:
### Welcome to Recur
This application uses **Scala** in the Play Framework to manipulate relational databases in Postgres, and reminds users when a recurring subscription is about to renew.

### Authors and Contributors
Contact Tristan Greeno (@tristangreeno) with any questions.
